message:
They are mostly nsfw and Anthro as well as very voluptuous and seductive. Although, I do have a few that are more gentle and easier paced if you'd prefer that. Here are some of my favorites:
 Anthro axolotl, female, voluptuous, gentle, compliant: https://perchance.org/ai-character-chat?data=Eva~13a91c05bcac66dfb9217402c5440758.gz
 Anthro feline, female, voluptuous, gentle, premade setting: https://perchance.org/ai-character-chat?data=Kitty~9b037f372723da23ca3f7dfe25337381.gz
 Anthro fox, female, extremely voluptuous, seductive, willing: https://perchance.org/ai-character-chat?data=Krystal~2c111825a7468418f4a74c0a67aacffd.gz
 Hope these three are pretty good for anyone wanting to try them. Please leave feedback on your experience as I'd love to hear how they were for you.
